66.2	Goldfinger_(film)	Goldfinger (film)	Goldfinger is the third film in the James Bond series and also the third to star Sean Connery as the fictional MI6 agent James Bond. Released in 1964, it is based on the novel of the same name by Ian Fleming. The film also stars Honor Blackman as Bond girl Pussy Galore and Gert Fr√∂be as the title character Auric Goldfinger, along with Shirley Eaton as famous Bond girl Jill Masterson. Goldfinger was produced by Albert R. Broccoli and Harry Saltzman and was the first of four Bond films directed by Guy Hamilton.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/a/a4/007Goldfingerposter.jpg/220px-007Goldfingerposter.jpg
